title: Getting Ready for Draft Week
description:
Kelsey, Mel, Keyshawn, and Darlington discuss what they are most looking forward to in next weeks NFL Draft, where do this years QBs land, which teams are open to trading up and down, and if Jared Goff is worried about the Lions drafting a QB.
